    "description": "<strong><u>To play Meta Quest 2, you must enter the game normally and select &quot;virtual reality&quot; when the option appears.</u></strong><br><br>你是TEMPUS的唯一居民，一个远离文明世界的小岛。在这里，你过着宁静无忧无虑的生活。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742590/extras/adcaf521349942c5a524b628ff09bb6b.poster.avif?t=1671183826\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742590/extras/adcaf521349942c5a524b628ff09bb6b.webm?t=1671183826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742590/extras/adcaf521349942c5a524b628ff09bb6b.mp4?t=1671183826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>但有一天晚上，一道耀眼的灯光出现，伴随着雷鸣般的声音。从那一刻起，一切都变了。你一靠近，灯光就消失了，显示出一个入口和一些基本指示。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742590/extras/3e06c51692b78aacaec5bbcd65290753.poster.avif?t=1671183826\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742590/extras/3e06c51692b78aacaec5bbcd65290753.webm?t=1671183826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742590/extras/3e06c51692b78aacaec5bbcd65290753.mp4?t=1671183826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当你进入时，你会发现这是一个时间旅行的门户，你会在200年后重新出现在家中。很快你就会意识到这是一次单程旅行，因为你不能回到过去，你只能向前旅行。<br><br><br>从那时起，你的目标是重新激活门户，以便你可以再次旅行并尝试了解正在发生的事情。你必须探索每个场景，以尝试恢复门户的能量，以便继续你的未知旅程。<br>TEMPUS是一部充满各种难题的冒险。它的特殊性在于，你会看到数千年来风景的变化。你会在你的岛上见证时间的影响<br><br>在这6个级别中，你会看到数百年来文明是如何变化的。<br>你能坚持到最后吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742590/extras/605e295617e088cff33433e3e6862215.poster.avif?t=1671183826\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742590/extras/605e295617e088cff33433e3e6862215.webm?t=1671183826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1742590/extras/605e295617e088cff33433e3e6862215.mp4?t=1671183826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
